{
  "texts": [
    "To continue ensuring inter-rater reliability at the screening on full text stage of 545 studies, three rounds of comparison coding were conducted (50, 30 and 30 items).",
    "The same two members of the team (MB and PP) responsible for screening the remaining items, again achieved almost perfect agreement (Cohen's k = 0.85) (McHugh, 2012), with synthesis.",
    "The reviews that only focus on higher education (or also continuing education) were then identified (n = 66) and will be the sole focus of the synthesis in this article.",
    "It should be noted that a further 32 reviews were identified that include a focus on higher education in some way (see OSF foot_1), i.e.",
    "the results are combined with other study levels such as K-12, but it was decided not to include them in this article, to ensure that all results pertain to higher education."
  ]
}